# Frontend Architecture (ai-writing-ui)

## Cấu trúc feature-based

```
src/
  api/
    client.ts              # Axios instance + interceptors + token helpers
    response.helpers.ts    # normalize response BE
    auth.service.ts        # 1 service = 1 module API
    writings.service.ts
    analytics.service.ts
    suggestions.service.ts
    users.service.ts
    index.ts               # barrel export services
  constants/
    index.ts
    api.constants.ts
    routes.constants.ts
    query-keys.constants.ts
    cache.constants.ts
    auth.constants.ts
  features/{module}/
    components/
    hooks/use{Module}Api.ts
    index.ts               # export components + hooks
  layouts/
  components/
    button/              # 1 folder = 1 component (xem components.mdc)
    input/
    loading/
    ...
    index.ts             # barrel export (tuỳ chọn)
```

**Không** dùng `components/ui/` gom nhiều file — xem rule `components.mdc`.

## Luồng gọi API (bắt buộc)

```
Component/Page → feature hook (useXxxApi) → module service (*.service.ts) → http (axios)
```

- **Axios chỉ** xuất hiện trong `api/client.ts` (export `http`).
- Service dùng `http` + `API_PATHS` từ constants; **không** hard-code URL.
- Component **không** import axios, **không** gọi `fetch`, **không** import `@/api` trực tiếp (trừ AuthContext).

```typescript
// ✅ api/writings.service.ts
export const writingsService = {
  getAll: (params) => http.get(..., API_PATHS.WRITINGS.ROOT, { params }),
};

// ✅ features/writings/hooks/useWritingsApi.ts
export function useWritings(params) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: QUERY_KEYS.writings.all(params),
    queryFn: () => writingsService.getAll(params),
    staleTime: CACHE_TIME.MEDIUM,
  });
}

// ✅ app/page hoặc component — import từ feature barrel
import { useWritings } from "@/features/writings";
```

## Component — một nhiệm vụ

- Tách component khi file > ~150 dòng hoặc có nhiều concern (form + list + modal → tách).
- `useState`/`useReducer` trong component chỉ cho **UI local** (modal open, tab active).
- State server (loading, data, error) đặt trong **hook** của module, không trong component.

## Import convention

- Page/component: `@/features/{module}` (barrel `index.ts`).
- Hook nội bộ feature: import service từ `@/api`, constants từ `@/constants`.
- **Cấm** file `src/hooks/useApi.ts` hoặc hook/API monolith tương tự.

## Hooks theo module

- File hook đặt tên `use{Module}Api.ts`: `useAuthApi`, `useWritingsApi`, `useAnalysisApi`, `useSuggestionsApi`.
- React Query keys lấy từ `QUERY_KEYS`; staleTime từ `CACHE_TIME`.
- Auth session state: `AuthContext` gọi `authService` + `usersService`, không gọi `http` trực tiếp.

## Constants FE

| File | Nội dung |
|------|----------|
| `api.constants.ts` | `API_PATHS`, `API_CONFIG` |
| `routes.constants.ts` | `ROUTES` |
| `query-keys.constants.ts` | `QUERY_KEYS` (factory functions) |
| `cache.constants.ts` | `CACHE_TIME` |
| `auth.constants.ts` | `AUTH_STORAGE_KEYS`, roles |
| `src/messages/` | Toàn bộ UI copy (label, toast, aria…) — xem `messages.mdc` |

## Page route (Next.js App Router)

- `app/**/page.tsx` mỏng: import hook/component từ `@/features/*`, không logic API nặng.

## Package manager

- **Yarn only** — xem `package-manager.mdc`. Không tạo `package-lock.json`.
